Class APXInterfaceDesignDescription

java.lang.Object
dto.APXInterfaceDesignDescription
public class APXInterfaceDesignDescription extends Object
The Interface Design Description (IDD) is a SysML stereotype that displays every service that a certain system provides including networking, format and security parameters.
Author:
fernand0labra
